 * calculations. Allows for greater control over the damage. (Drop pods, anyone?)
 *
 * @param	levels_fallen How many Z-levels the atom has fallen before landing
 * on its current loc.
 *
 * @return	A two entity list: list(weight, fall_force)
 */
